  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective chart review/data collection study of natural orifice translumenal
      endoscopic surgery (NOTES) for sleeve gastrectomy, that will include questionnaires
      administered throughout the study. Subjects enrolled will be those intending to have a
      transvaginal NOTES sleeve gastrectomy. Data will be collected and reviewed through 12 months
      post-op.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
